description:
Danny welcomes Julie Plake McMinn from Bethenny Ever After to discuss her time on the show, what she learned working alongside Bethenny, and lots more! Danny also chats with Mindy Cohn, who currently stars in A Nice Girl Like You (avail onDemand) and is previously known for her role as Natalie on the iconic The Facts of Life.


WATCH the interviews on YouTube at YouTube.com/DannyPellegrino1

Julie website: www.julieplakemcminn.com
